<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/AFJAND-Volume-11-No.-4-2011" title="AFJAND Volume 11 No. 4 (2011)" alt="link">AFJAND Volume 11 No. 4 (2011)</a></h2>

	
					<p><a href="http://www.ajfand.net/Volume11/No4/index4.html%20" target="_blank">This issue</a> of the African Journal of Food, Agriculture, Nutrition and Development (AFJAND) focuses on nutrition, compiling peer reviewed articles on dietary diversity and nutritional status of very young children and lactating mothers in a number of African countries.</p>
							<p><span class="date">21/09/2011</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/AFJAND-Volume-11-No.-4-2011">Read more...</a>
